Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.93,0:23:49.65,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1223)}希望大家能笑得更加開心 my mind
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.31,0:00:08.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更加激烈的大魔斗比武最終的戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.90,0:00:10.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這其中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.23,0:00:13.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在身負特別任務的夏面前出現的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.28,0:00:15.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是從未來來的露西
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.03,0:00:19.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她宣告了恐怖的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.70,0:00:24.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,另一方面 公主翡翠為了和超過一萬頭龍的龍群作戰
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.96,0:00:28.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啟動了日蝕2計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.59,0:00:34.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏他們為了迴避黑暗的未來 開始尋找突破口
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.32,0:02:23.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然使用…兩種屬性
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.54,0:02:29.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伽吉魯那傢伙 什麼時候能夠達到這種程度了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.96,0:02:33.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然這也是在預想之外 但沒什麼不好的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.09,0:02:36.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然吸收的影的屬性
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.30,0:02:40.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,變得和怪物一樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.43,0:02:42.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖說他本來就有這樣的素質
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.18,0:02:49.02,Title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3\pos(640,450)\fad(524,0}激雷 !
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.27,0:02:56.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 這種情況之前沒有交代過
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.40,0:02:58.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,究竟是怎樣一種情況呢 矢島先生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.94,0:03:01.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然無法料想啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.82,0:03:05.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是不知道滅龍魔法師到底有多深
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.20,0:03:09.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不不 羅格選手是第三代滅龍魔法師南瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.58,0:03:12.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還不到結局 精彩從現在開始南瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.92,0:03:17.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此 也就是鐵影龍嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.93,0:03:22.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.14,0:03:25.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 是化身為影子了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.47,0:03:28.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然這樣 我也用同樣的魔法好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.14,0:03:34.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太天真了 在那裏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.15,0:03:42.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.45,0:03:45.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兩個人都化身為影子了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.62,0:03:47.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這會變成怎樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.49,0:03:49.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全分不清誰是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.50,0:03:54.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 好厲害 南瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.38,0:03:56.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經完全不知道是怎麼回事了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.42,0:03:59.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經不知道該怎麼報道實況了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.63,0:04:03.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總之 不管怎樣都很厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.22,0:04:07.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.35,0:04:09.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能看見麼 畢古斯羅
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.68,0:04:12.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,透過監視器判斷有些困難
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.89,0:04:16.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 應該是速度快的一方是伽吉魯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.44,0:04:17.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.44,0:04:20.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.07,0:04:23.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要從影子裏被拽出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.72,0:04:51.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我所不知道的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.85,0:04:52.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伽吉魯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.52,0:04:54.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,消失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.48,0:05:01.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鐵影龍的咆哮
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.86,0:05:47.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勝負…勝負已分 勝負已分
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.62,0:05:55.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勝者是伽吉魯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.71,0:05:59.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,羅格輸了 南瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.54,0:06:01.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 真是精彩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.75,0:06:03.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 到現在為止
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.38,0:06:06.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妖精的尾巴再得一分 總分51分
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.80,0:06:09.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,劍咬之虎是55分
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.55,0:06:12.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是可以一點一點幹上來的 南瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.89,0:06:21.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對現在的羅格來說 這種程度就是極限了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.56,0:06:23.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.70,0:06:32.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,消失了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.70,0:06:34.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要再打了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.62,0:06:37.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.12,0:06:41.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,羅格會死的 請不要再打了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.38,0:06:50.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勝負已分 我不會再動手了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.68,0:06:56.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弗洛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.18,0:06:59.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,羅格 羅格
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.31,0:07:00.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼…你會在這裏？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.64,0:07:02.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,羅格
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.15,0:07:03.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.90,0:07:08.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？ 身體怎麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.99,0:07:13.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我輸了嗎…好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.99,0:07:16.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不記得了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.08,0:07:22.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個影子…到底是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.33,0:07:26.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 真是滅龍魔法師之間的駭人的戰鬥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.80,0:07:30.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,與預想的展開不同 真是很厲害啊南瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.92,0:07:33.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是大魔斗比武的樂趣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.84,0:07:34.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.85,0:07:37.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經向好的方面發展了呢 初代
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.64,0:07:38.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.35,0:07:44.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,邪惡的影子 我所不知道的魔力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.44,0:07:54.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火龍的翼擊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.62,0:07:56.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷古勒斯的衝擊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.87,0:08:00.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天龍的咆哮
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.75,0:08:03.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,增援還沒來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.33,0:08:05.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正從7 8區向這裏移動
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.63,0:08:07.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣的話 就以數量壓上去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.75,0:08:08.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要阻止他們
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.63,0:08:10.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了翡翠公主
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.09,0:08:12.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要抓住他們
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.18,0:08:16.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底有多少啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.80,0:08:18.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不該走這條路的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.18,0:08:21.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然能用魔法的話 應該沒事的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.93,0:08:24.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏露露 很危險的你退後
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.27,0:08:25.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.36,0:08:28.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,危險
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.07,0:08:32.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我噴 此路不通
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.07,0:08:33.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢伙是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.99,0:08:35.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,惡狼騎士團的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.28,0:08:36.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.66,0:08:40.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們還在執行任務喲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.58,0:08:46.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,HI 還記得我的名字嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.79,0:08:47.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.67,0:08:49.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 在這個時機…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.71,0:08:53.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要小看王國最強的處刑人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.38,0:08:54.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說 卡咪卡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.63,0:08:56.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個恐怖的女人不在哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.18,0:08:58.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大 大
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.51,0:09:01.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿喲 嘿喲 嘿喲 嘿喲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.14,0:09:03.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,協會的魔法師們啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.44,0:09:07.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們的理念我已經十分清楚了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.90,0:09:11.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在開始我要貫徹我們的理念了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.32,0:09:15.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是決不讓犯人活著離開城堡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.03,0:09:18.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真纏人 可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.49,0:09:21.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快 快
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.49,0:09:24.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,惡狼騎士團已經向這個方向追過去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.50,0:09:25.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就放心了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.08,0:09:27.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們也快去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.98,0:09:52.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿魯卡迪歐斯大佐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.03,0:09:54.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您為什麼在這裏…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.86,0:09:57.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您不是有叛國嫌疑…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.24,0:10:00.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,公主在哪裏？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.95,0:10:01.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.58,0:10:04.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在哪裏？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.00,0:10:06.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在…在最頂層…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.17,0:10:12.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 那個鎧甲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.09,0:10:13.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 那個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.67,0:10:15.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白百合之鎧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.67,0:10:17.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戰鬥用的鎧甲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.34,0:10:19.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個人告訴了我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.26,0:10:22.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日蝕的另一種使用方法
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.01,0:10:24.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日蝕2
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.72,0:10:27.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,2？ 那到底是？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.68,0:10:31.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這7年間我們利用大魔斗比武
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.31,0:10:33.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為這扇門積累了不少魔力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.44,0:10:40.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通過這種方法收集的魔力可以和魔法精靈力相媲美
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.99,0:10:45.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什…竟然可以和魔法評議院擁有的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.91,0:10:50.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,據說可以毀滅一個國家的神聖之光媲美
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.42,0:10:53.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,將這個力量向龍群發射
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.21,0:10:57.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是日蝕2計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.13,0:11:03.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,街上都是為大魔斗比武攝影的魔水晶屏
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.97,0:11:07.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想從地下走和傑拉爾他們匯合
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.35,0:11:08.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,傑拉爾？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.10,0:11:10.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我把一切都和他坦白了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.31,0:11:14.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在 他應該在思考對策
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.82,0:11:16.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在思考對策？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.03,0:11:18.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.36,0:11:29.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒能從未來帶來解決這件事的對策
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.41,0:11:32.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有件事必須要確認一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.71,0:11:39.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那並不是說謊者的眼淚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.67,0:11:42.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說謊的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.47,0:11:44.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是公主
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.82,0:12:02.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大魔斗比武最終戰 也終於到了高潮呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.53,0:12:05.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一名 是劍咬之虎 55分
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.37,0:12:07.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第二名 是妖精的尾巴 51分
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.99,0:12:11.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第三名 是蛇姬之鱗 49分 南瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.79,0:12:16.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伽吉魯的勝利讓妖精的尾巴追了上來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.21,0:12:20.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 劍齒之虎只剩下斯汀選手和米涅芭選手了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.67,0:12:23.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要打敗他們也很難 南瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.93,0:12:26.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,斯汀選手在什麼地方呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.64,0:12:29.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概是有什麼作戰計劃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.89,0:12:30.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你個賤人…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.22,0:12:33.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下一個就是你了 艾露莎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.27,0:12:36.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 從你的傷勢就能分出勝負了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.99,0:12:46.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾露莎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.12,0:12:48.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,貌似不行了 可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.12,0:12:51.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,腳上的傷很嚴重啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.83,0:12:57.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 妖精女王艾露莎的大危機啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.71,0:12:59.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無法抵擋米涅芭的猛攻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.46,0:13:04.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被拔去羽毛的妖精 真是不像樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.72,0:13:07.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多該到高潮了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.39,0:13:11.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來進行妖精女王的公開處刑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.85,0:13:15.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站起來 站起來啊 艾露莎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.19,0:13:18.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火花四射的最終戰
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.90,0:13:25.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,另外 這邊是冰之造型魔法的對決
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.82,0:13:27.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真能打啊 灰
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.70,0:13:29.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總之先表揚你一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.87,0:13:32.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別說這些不痛不癢的 裏恩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.08,0:13:36.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,茱比亞
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.96,0:13:39.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 水流升霞
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.67,0:13:42.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冰凝 短槍
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.38,0:13:45.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天神之舞
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.43,0:13:47.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,漂亮 雪莉婭
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.68,0:13:49.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別發呆啊 裏恩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.18,0:13:51.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.51,0:13:56.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然用朱比亞的水來攻擊 真是骯髒的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.18,0:13:57.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在說什麼啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.98,0:14:01.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的骯髒不適合茱比亞 給我讓開
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.73,0:14:02.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.44,0:14:03.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,裏恩真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.94,0:14:05.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冰凝 蛟
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.82,0:14:09.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灰大人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.37,0:14:14.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,裏恩 你也攻擊茱比亞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.41,0:14:16.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就交給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.62,0:14:19.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 不許傷到她
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.17,0:14:19.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.21,0:14:22.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,裏恩大人有這麼強嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.30,0:14:25.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 你們完全沒有配合
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.42,0:14:28.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到處是破綻
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.72,0:14:30.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這邊變成持久戰了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.26,0:14:33.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您覺得怎麼樣 矢島先生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.22,0:14:36.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灰和裏恩都是好男人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.73,0:14:38.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒問你這個南瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.10,0:14:42.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過優勝肯定是雪莉婭親拿下了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.61,0:14:43.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.69,0:14:49.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上啊上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.91,0:14:53.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地形效果 熱風帶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.45,0:14:59.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這不是來了熱攻擊嗎 我燃起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.87,0:15:00.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.38,0:15:06.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大大 地形效果 冰山帶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.34,0:15:09.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是麻煩的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.43,0:15:14.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂 連你也一起融化掉哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.89,0:15:18.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是滅龍魔法師吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.73,0:15:20.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯啊 怎麼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.73,0:15:26.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天龍的翼擊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.86,0:15:29.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像值得一融呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.24,0:15:31.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紙吹雪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.70,0:15:33.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赤之舞
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.99,0:15:38.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開啟吧 天蝎座的門扉 斯科皮恩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.87,0:15:40.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.21,0:15:41.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交給我吧 Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.83,0:15:45.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黃色的紙是雷之神
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.79,0:15:47.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沙風暴
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.63,0:15:51.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是星靈魔法嗎 攻擊力不錯嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.72,0:15:53.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是叫科斯莫斯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.34,0:15:56.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不想和可愛的女生戰鬥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.35,0:15:57.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從今天開始做朋友…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.18,0:16:05.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我最討厭臉皮厚的男生了 這是對美的褻瀆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.77,0:16:06.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以消失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.86,0:16:10.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯嗯 突然這樣可能有點緊張了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.49,0:16:12.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,害羞的時候也很可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.70,0:16:13.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才不是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.57,0:16:16.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 這樣如何
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.70,0:16:18.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是我送你的禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.91,0:16:21.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我就以這個回禮
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.16,0:16:23.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,孢子炸彈 林卡雷卡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.62,0:16:24.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.46,0:16:25.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是處刑人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.92,0:16:28.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 我們也幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.63,0:16:30.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼可能讓你們得逞
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.51,0:16:41.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,貓軍人啊 我聽說你之前是軍人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.77,0:16:45.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼捨棄國家加入魔法師協會？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.56,0:16:50.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和你說你也不會懂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.48,0:16:51.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概能猜到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.90,0:16:54.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是值得你奉獻忠義的國家吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.86,0:16:56.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,注意你的言辭 處刑人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.12,0:16:59.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不允許有人蔑視艾德拉斯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.54,0:17:07.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大大 怎麼了大？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.58,0:17:09.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,累了大？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.63,0:17:12.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,累不累的都沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.84,0:17:16.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們上幾個人也沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.64,0:17:20.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們只是要突破這裏 僅此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.26,0:17:26.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管來多少阻礙 都別想攔住妖精的尾巴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.27,0:17:30.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各 各位 請看這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.52,0:17:32.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,南瓜 來了來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.73,0:17:35.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聖十大魔法師的鳩拉南瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.61,0:17:40.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老夫也可以摻一腳吧 久違地熱血沸騰了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.20,0:17:45.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出現了啊 怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.54,0:17:48.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在開始才是動真格的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.75,0:17:54.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鳩拉出場 蛇姬之鱗就穩贏了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.21,0:17:57.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管是拉克薩斯還是奧爾加就弱如襁褓中嬰兒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.84,0:18:00.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是說他們運氣不好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.64,0:18:02.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太強了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.10,0:18:03.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,激動個啥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.56,0:18:05.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明瞬間就輸了 給我轉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.56,0:18:07.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經在轉了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.24,0:18:19.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是怎樣的壓迫力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.20,0:18:21.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事的 能行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.03,0:18:24.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在這裏哦 拉克薩斯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.16,0:18:26.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷神眾都和你在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.29,0:18:28.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個拉克薩斯在緊張？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.29,0:18:35.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鳩拉 我想看看你認真的樣子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.76,0:18:36.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.89,0:18:43.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來接這招試試 你有那膽子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.47,0:18:47.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是雷的滅神魔法師
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.60,0:18:53.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,滅神魔法和聖十的稱號哪個比較強 誰都會想知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.90,0:18:55.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼樣 聖十的魔法師
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.74,0:18:58.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能擋下來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.61,0:19:01.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是說聖十隻是個名頭罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.49,0:19:04.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.45,0:19:10.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這傢伙 給大叔設了個圈套
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.83,0:19:12.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,受人挑撥了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.63,0:19:13.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好騙了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.88,0:19:15.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,煩死了 給我轉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.80,0:19:18.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經在轉了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.59,0:19:23.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接招吧 雷神的符電粒子炮
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.53,0:19:41.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.41,0:19:45.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在第一天的比賽中
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.66,0:19:52.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一擊就解決了戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.37,0:19:54.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真 真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.75,0:00:00.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怪物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.21,0:19:58.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蛇 蛇姬之鱗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.84,0:20:01.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以一分之差對妖精的尾巴緊咬不放
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.47,0:20:06.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這 這下沒戲了…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.60,0:20:08.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在說什麼啊 會長
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.68,0:20:10.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我相信拉克薩斯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.85,0:20:13.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拉克薩斯即使面對鳩拉 也能超越過去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.19,0:20:15.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.32,0:20:22.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放棄吧 馬卡洛夫
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.65,0:20:25.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在你不在的七年間
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.53,0:20:29.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鳩拉已經上升到了聖十大魔法師的第五位
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.66,0:20:33.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然無論怎樣也無法追上上面的四個人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.67,0:20:36.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別說他們了 給我骨碌碌地轉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.71,0:20:39.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經在轉了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.76,0:20:42.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊修迦爾四天王…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.88,0:20:45.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些傢伙不是人類
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.39,0:20:50.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是說 鳩拉是人類最強的魔法師
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.47,0:20:51.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鳩拉·雷吉斯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.56,0:20:56.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是這場最終戰中我最警戒的對手
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.02,0:21:00.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼都不用說了 拉克薩斯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.69,0:21:02.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我看到最後吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.24,0:21:09.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我曾經和你交手過一次吧 馬卡洛夫的…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.49,0:21:11.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等下 接下來別說了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.58,0:21:19.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站在這裏的不是牛逼稱號的大叔也不是誰的孫子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.84,0:21:21.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是兩個男人罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.34,0:21:24.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,眼神不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.67,0:22:01.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又 又是一擊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.38,0:22:03.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道要說什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.71,0:22:04.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厲害南瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.51,0:22:07.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,角色設定錯了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.97,0:22:11.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世上人外有人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.72,0:22:14.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這我非常清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.35,0:22:19.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 偶爾也該看看下邊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.73,0:22:23.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也許馬上就追到腳邊了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.24,0:24:00.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大魔斗比武 終於快要結束了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.33,0:24:03.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 感覺終於要比完了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.79,0:24:06.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還真是打了好久呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.29,0:24:07.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 是的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.96,0:24:10.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剩下的儘是一堆高手
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.51,0:24:12.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過一定會沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.18,0:24:16.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是當然 勝出的肯定是我們妖精的尾巴
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.72,0:24:18.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下集 GLORIA
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.60,0:24:21.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家再加點油 取得勝利吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.77,0:24:24.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最後一戰 不要輸哦

